file.name: MarkerPosition.yaml
file.content:
info:
  title: BrAPI
  version: ''
openapi: 3.0.0
paths: {}
components: 
  schemas:
    MarkerPosition: 
      type: object 
      properties:
        additionalInfo:
          additionalProperties:
            type: string
          description: Additional arbitrary info
          type: object
        mapDbId:
          description: The unique ID of the map 
          type: string
          example: 3d52bdf3
        mapName: 
          description: The human readable name of the map
          type: string
          example: Genome Map 1
        linkageGroupName: 
          description: The Uniquely Identifiable name of this linkage group
          type: string
          example: Chromosome 3 
        position: 
          description: The position of a marker within a linkage group
          type: integer
          example: 2390
        variantDbId: 
          description: Internal db identifier
          type: string
          example: a1eb250a
        variantName: 
          description: The human readable name for a marker
          type: string
          example: Marker_2390
